(70145, 205177, 0, 1, 'Santa baby (cover)', 'Zero：這是我們精心準備的聖誕禮物，祝大家聖誕節快樂！', '2013-12-24 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 2, 4, 'Santa baby, slip a sable under the tree, for me\nI''ve been an awful good girl\nSanta baby, and hurry down the chimney tonight\n\nSanta baby, an fifty-four convertible too, light blue\nI''ll wait up for you dear\nSanta baby, and hurry down the chimney tonight\n\nThink of all the fun i''ve missed\nThink of all the fellas that i haven''t kissed\nNext year i could be oh so good\nIf you''d check off my christmas list\nBoo doo bee doo\n\nSanta honey, i wanna yacht and really that''s\nNot a lot\nI''ve been an awful good girl\nSanta baby, and hurry down the chimney tonight\n\nSanta cutie, there''s one thing i really do need, the deed\nTo a platinum mine\nSanta cutie, and hurry down the chimney tonight\n\nSanta baby, i''m filling my stocking with a duplex, and checks\nSign your ''x'' on the line\nSanta baby, and hurry down the chimney tonight\n\nCome and trim my christmas tree\nWith some decorations bought at tiffany''s\nI really do believe in you\nLet''s see if you believe in me\nBoo doo bee doo\n\nSanta baby, forgot to mention one little thing, a ring\nI don''t mean a phone\nSanta baby, and hurry down the chimney tonight\nHurry down the chimney tonight\nHurry \ntonight!', '', 219, '', 'Eartha Kitt', 'Eartha Kitt', 'Nightcap 睡帽樂團', 'Nightcap 睡帽樂團', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-12-25 01:36:32', '2015-03-12 14:04:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(70146, 6687, 5473, 4, '舉頭三呎有神明', '', '2012-12-30 00:00:00', 2000, 19, 2, 1, '舉頭三尺有神明，神明近視看不清，\n手腳冰冷四肢無力，該是退休的年齡。\n\n你六根不清靜，眼睛長在頭頂，\n做事要腳踏實地，做人憑良心；\n別迷信別嘴硬，有病就去看病，\n不要再拖下去，腦殘沒藥醫。\n\n睡夢羅漢，地藏王菩薩，\n釋迦牟尼，藥師如來，\n四十二章經，菩提老祖，佛啊佛啊！\n文昌帝君，城隍威靈公，\n全真七子，玄天上帝，\n中國古拳法，萬佛朝宗，神啊神啊！\n\n舉頭三尺有神明，神明近視看不清，\n手腳冰冷四肢無力，該是退休的年齡；\n舉頭三尺有神明，神明說他看不清，\n人們虛偽戴著面具，到底是誰有心機。\n\n神明來我夢裡，終於把我打醒，\n人都會有報應，善惡要分明；\n花錢消災解運，只想求個安心，\n點燈來放光明，留言當放屁。\n\n舉頭三尺有神明，神明近視看不清，\n做人總是昧著良心，你的信仰在哪裡；\n舉頭三尺有神明，神明說他看不清，\n抬頭尋找祢閉著眼睛，舉頭三尺操你媽個屄。', '', 254, '', '', '', '', '神棍樂團', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-12-25 02:53:40', '2015-03-12 14:04:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
